::KitKat::

She went to the entrance after DarkMouse was put into a CR chamber.
She needed to clear her head before company came.  No such luck. She 
heard the voice calling out to her.  She opened her link on the 
general Pred frequence. "Approach and be recognized.  I an KitKat. 
Please come to the entrance and I shall see you there." She walked 
over and stood in the open entrance way. waiting for the bot to come 
to her.
